        {
            "title": "台股開升   最多升1.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台股加權平均指數今早高開0.5%，報19609.90點。現升170點或0.87%，報19692。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">最高見19727，升214點或1.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/09/20230704_FI_source-licensed_台股-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/09/20230704_FI_source-licensed_台股-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">AI晶片大廠英偉達14日宣布，與台積電、鴻海、緯創、艾克爾(Amkor)、日月光投控旗下矽品等製造夥伴合作，首度在美國設廠生產AI超級電腦，預計未來4年將在美國生產價值高達5000億美元的AI基礎設施。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台積電升0.92%，報873元新台幣；鴻海跌0.726%，報137.5元新台幣。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14855291-%e5%8f%b0%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%8d%87-%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a%e5%8d%871-1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230704_FI_source-licensed_TaiwanStock.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 09:35:59",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指開市跌2點 深成指升1點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段變動不大，上證綜指以3260點開市，跌2點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報9886點，升1點或0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌2點或0.07%，開報3756點；創業板指數開市報1933點，升不足1點或0.05%。</p>\n</div>",
